description: Democratic political strategist James Carville, who has been openly critical of the Harris campaign since Democrats’ 2024 election losses, reflected on his failed prediction that Vice President Harris would win against President-elect Trump, calling it “very depressing.” In an interview Saturday with CNN’s Michael Smerconish, Carville was asked about a recent op-ed in The New…
title: Carville reflects on failed prediction that Harris would defeat Trump: ‘Very depressing’
